Structural Divergence Analysis

Maria Laura Marcos, Julian Echave

Introduction

In this case we studied the globins family. We used as reference for the ENM the protein with pdb code 1a4fb. We simulated 10 mutants of this reference for each protein of the family. The globins family is of the type alpha and consists of the following proteins:
